description: Submission of reserved matters relating to external appearance and landscaping for Buildings F, G & H, pursuant to hybrid planning permission ref: 2011/00407/COMB granted 23rd December 2011, comprising a mixed use development of 223 new homes (1,365 sqm GIA) of ground floor commercial floor space (use classes A1-A4, B1, D1 & D2),  landscaped open space and parking provision.
